// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0550 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f75d2e46-3614-5584-ba01-54adc86fae2e

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:16.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.10*")
